{"tid":170654,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[深夜叫春] 有冇人發覺世代交替緊？","createTime":"2017-03-24T21:53:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T22:20:42.000Z","uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ee5fe4425610a2a7e96fa3531fc6bcd551234aa4","tid":170654,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T21:53:56.000Z","msg":"當你見到茶餐廳部電視一開TVB就出現<br />\n當你見到亞視《百萬富翁》 爛gag「我讀drama架」「8千大元」可以仍然有人睇唔明（睇唔明都似世界觀只有TVB既00後為多）<br />\n有冇人突然發覺自己有D老態<br />\n由自稱 TV版友 到 高登仔 再到 連登仔 唔系話扮老屎忽 只係覺得屬於自己果個年代慢慢都開始過去 新一批又開始浮面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 世代一直都轉變緊 今日你仲笑「仆你個街，亞視黎既！」 過多幾日可能問返你「亞視 系咩黎ha <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」"},{"pid":"fa4dfd5803ccf4f832884870ce2bb532168a6fe4","tid":170654,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T22:07:54.000Z","msg":"你睇下連登咁多小學雞就知啦"},{"pid":"cda8a6b549077814a00b9bc597cd4eb6ea52baa2","tid":170654,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T22:11:47.000Z","msg":"我記得5-6年前你成日係高登打簡體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d98b46402330ffa6b1d7d41ddffa72c06db306eb","tid":170654,"uid":90529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T22:13:22.000Z","msg":"同啲95 96 打後後既講周星馳啲電影對白，十個得一個係接得上。"},{"pid":"dc0adfa96ab80ac8cc748c2257d92e20fef47931","tid":170654,"uid":15646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T22:17:50.000Z","msg":"系你老母咩返5p啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83de0462c1014447c1421dea641c6b2cd29694a","tid":170654,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T22:20:42.000Z","msg":"原post<br />\n[深夜叫春］有無人發覺世代交替緊？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/170578?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/170578?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}